    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-display-xl text-primary mb-8">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
    <div class="space-y-6 text-sm text-body-text leading-relaxed">
      <p>Last updated: July 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mt-8">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>By accessing or using ALL Youtube Download ("the Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms &amp; Conditions. If you do not agree, please do not use the Service.</p>

