      <p>ALL Youtube Download is a free web-based utility that allows users to download YouTube video thumbnails and media streams. The Service processes publicly available content through automated tools and does not host or store any media files.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mt-8">3. User Responsibilities</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
