      <p>The Service is provided "as is" without any warranty, express or implied. We shall not be liable for any damages arising from the use or inability to use the Service, including but not limited to direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mt-8">6. No Guarantee of Service</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue the Service at any time without notice. We are not responsible for any downtime, data loss, or service interruptions.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mt-8">7. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>The Service integrates with third-party tools and APIs including yt-dlp, YouTube oEmbed, and CORS proxy services. We are not responsible for the availability, reliability, or actions of these third-party services.</p>

